36#include "kadm5_locl.h"
37
38__RCSID("$NetBSD: rename_c.c,v 1.2 2017/01/28 21:31:49 christos Exp $");
39
40kadm5_ret_t
41kadm5_c_rename_principal(void *server_handle,
42 krb5_principal source,
43 krb5_principal target)
44{
45 kadm5_client_context *context = server_handle;
46 kadm5_ret_t ret;
47 krb5_storage *sp;
48 unsigned char buf[1024];
49 int32_t tmp;
50 krb5_data reply;
51
52 ret = _kadm5_connect(server_handle);
53 if(ret)
54 return ret;
55
56 sp = krb5_storage_from_mem(buf, sizeof(buf));
57 if (sp == NULL)
58 return ENOMEM;
59 krb5_store_int32(sp, kadm_rename);
60 krb5_store_principal(sp, source);
61 krb5_store_principal(sp, target);
62 ret = _kadm5_client_send(context, sp);
63 krb5_storage_free(sp);
64 if (ret)
65 return ret;
66 ret = _kadm5_client_recv(context, &reply);
67 if(ret)
68 return ret;
69 sp = krb5_storage_from_data (&reply);
70 if (sp == NULL) {
71 krb5_data_free (&reply);
72 return ENOMEM;
73 }
74 krb5_ret_int32(sp, &tmp);
75 ret = tmp;
76 krb5_storage_free(sp);
77 krb5_data_free (&reply);
78 return ret;
79}
